                " SCINTILLATION COUNTING TECHNIQUES. SEPERATE",
                " EXPERIMENTS USED TO CHECK FOR TRITIUM ACTIVITY",
                " DETERMINATION REPRODUCABILITY AND SERIOUS SYSTEMATIC",
                " ERRORS OF MEASUREMENT TECHNIQUES. CONVERSION OF DATA",
